						<p><hi rend="bold">Pāṇḍya, Kulasekara-Pāṇḍya, Year 13 = c. 13th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mutilated. Seems to record a royal order, communicated by the officer Maḻavarāyaṉ to the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Chōḻakulāntaka-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, relating to some tax concession.</p>						

